---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon'

const features = [
  {
    name: 'Easy to Create Content',
    description:
      'Create pages and blog posts using MDX (Markdown with Javascript components). Includes support for math equations (KaTeX) and diagrams (mermaid, plantuml and markmap)',
    icon: 'sparkles',
  },
  {
    name: 'Customisable Design',
    description:
      'Built using the TailwindCSS ecosystem (including HeroIcons and Hero Patterns). Very easy to customise and change design. Template illustrations by unDraw.',
    icon: 'puzzle',
  },
  {
    name: 'SEO Ready',
    description:
      'Full support for Facebook (Open Graph), Twitter Cards, Schema/JSON-LD metadata. Automatically generated robots.txt, RSS feed and sitemap.',
    icon: 'presentation-chart-bar',
  },
  {
    name: 'Blazing Performance',
    description:
      'Achieve great web vitals scores. Static site using Jamstack architecture. Built using Astro and Typescript for ultimate performance and type safety.',
    icon: 'clock',
  },
]
---

<div class="py-12 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-zinc-800">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="lg:text-center">
      <h2
        class="text-base text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-300 font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase"
      >
        Partner with us
      </h2>
      <p
        class="mt-2 text-xl leading-8 font-black tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 sm:text-4xl"
      >
      Partnering with RnDAO is for you if:
      </p>
      <ul class="flex flex-col space-y-5 mt-4 mx-auto max-w-fit text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 lg:mx-auto text-left">
        <li class="pl-0 inline-flex items-center">
          <Icon
          class="h-12 w-12 mr-3 flex-none "
          aria-hidden="true"
          pack="heroicons-outline"
          name="check"
        />
        <span>You are working in a challenging market</span></li>
        <li class="pl-0 inline-flex items-center justify-start">
          <Icon
          class="h-12 w-12 mr-3 flex-none"
          aria-hidden="true"
          pack="heroicons-outline"
          name="check"
        />
        <span>You have a new idea, and want to know how to position it so it’s valued instead of ignored</span></li>
        <li class="pl-0 inline-flex items-center">
          <Icon
          class="h-12 w-12 mr-3 flex-none"
          aria-hidden="true"
          pack="heroicons-outline"
          name="check"
        />
        <span>Sales and adoption haven’t picked up as hoped, and you want to know why</span></li>
        <li class="pl-0 inline-flex items-center">
          <Icon
          class="h-12 w-12 mr-3 flex-none"
          aria-hidden="true"
          pack="heroicons-outline"
          name="check"
        />
        <span>You have a hunch about the solution that's needed, and don't want to waste time building the wrong thing</span></li>
        <li class="pl-0 inline-flex items-center">
          <Icon
          class="h-12 w-12 mr-3 flex-none"
          aria-hidden="true"
          pack="heroicons-outline"
          name="check"
        />
        <span>You need to know where you should build on your own, and where you should partner with others</span></li>
        <li class="pl-0 inline-flex items-center">
          <Icon
          class="h-12 w-12 mr-3 flex-none"
          aria-hidden="true"
          pack="heroicons-outline"
          name="check"
        />
        <span>You want a sounding board you can trust to think through all the details</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

